Resource Profile: HCIM BloodPressure

Official URL: http://nictiz.nl/fhir/StructureDefinition/zib-BloodPressure Version: 1.3.15
Active as of 2024-04-09 Computable Name: Zib BloodPressure

Copyright/Legal: CC0

This profile is derived from the HL7 Vital Signs profile for Blood Pressure in order to add mappings from the Dutch Health and Care Information models (Dutch: Zorginformatiebouwsteen or ZIB) BloodPresurre version 3.1, release 2017 and to provide extensions for missing concepts if needed.

The blood pressure is a parameter for determining the condition of the blood circulation and is expressed in systolic and diastolic pressure in mmHg.

Blood pressure is measured to gain an indication of the health condition of the patient’s cardiovascular system.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Observation/zib-bloodpressure-01
